{"tid":2457672,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"外國傳媒選「最性感女星」， Jennie美貌更勝「黑寡婦」等荷里活女神 ⊙.⊙","createTime":"2021-03-22T23:34:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T05:44:38.000Z","uid":44730,"like":7,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2c05dfb548ce0a75722bdaca8557edab7975bd9b","tid":2457672,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T23:34:48.000Z","msg":"自08年「韓流」興盛以來，韓劇、韓星、韓樂都在全世界打開知名度，頗具人氣，像是《雖然是精神病但沒關係》、《屍戰朝鮮2》、《愛的迫降》等話題韓劇都多次登上《時代雜誌》、《紐約時報》等國際版面，偶像團體BTS、BLACKPINK、SuperM都多次登上歐美脫口節目，甚至奪下國際獎項。近日，美媒票選「全球最性感女星」，結果出爐後，擁有人間香奈兒之稱的Jennie竟自一票荷里活大咖女神中脫穎而出，奪下亞軍寶座。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CMuuLguDSbl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCMuuLguDSbl&d=VfnGJYDpQhHIir2SHpwXXE2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=8cee025c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCMuuLguDSbl&h=c1ddb6ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CMuuLguDSbl</a><br />\n荷里活造型&hellip; 😄"},{"pid":"bd315896a6486d7f55a4e6d67e447399ba7501ff","tid":2457672,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T23:35:01.000Z","msg":"自2016年出道以來一直都是媒體的焦點，每次推出新歌都橫掃各大音源榜，也曾與杜娃黎波、女神卡卡、賽琳娜戈梅茲等多位歐美知名歌手合作，而她們的高人氣、獨特的時尚品味，還讓她們成為各大時尚品牌的寵兒，其中Jennie還因時尚的穿搭、慵懶魅惑的高級臉、火辣姣好的身材獲得香奈兒的代言，被媒體譽為是「人間香奈兒」，此次奪下亞軍寶座讓人不禁讚嘆她的高人氣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2021/03/22/1/11921777.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2021%2F03%2F22%2F1%2F11921777.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=07ffddc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2021/03/22/1/11921776.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2021%2F03%2F22%2F1%2F11921776.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=8a772021&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4151b17c64b152f19e5ec8ab47a68b91a4d3915e","tid":2457672,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T23:35:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2021/03/22/1/11921775.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2021%2F03%2F22%2F1%2F11921775.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=c79f2046&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除了Jennie外，曾多次被票選為世界性感女性的漫威女神「黑寡婦」史嘉蕾喬韓森（Scarlett Johansson）、天后蕾哈娜（Rihanna）都憑藉著凹凸有致的性感曲線，登上此榜，而獲得冠軍后位的就是奪下艾美獎最年輕視后的「新蜘蛛女」千黛亞（Zendaya）。"},{"pid":"d54753559238fdad72e500502ae343955e57216f","tid":2457672,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T23:35:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2021/03/22/1/11921779.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2021%2F03%2F22%2F1%2F11921779.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=2b4e279b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2021/03/22/1/11921778.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2021%2F03%2F22%2F1%2F11921778.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=a6c6da79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1996年生，今年才24歲的千黛亞（Zendaya）12歲時就以童裝模特身分出道，而後出演迪士尼情境喜劇《舞動青春》、《麻辣特工》、《蜘蛛人》系列電影，成為新一代荷里活女神，還在去年憑藉《Euphoria》獲得艾美獎最佳劇情類影集女主角獎。不只演技備受肯定，千黛亞擁有德國、蘇格蘭等多國血統，出眾的混血外貌、178公分的高挑身材，不僅讓她擁有超強的時尚駕馭力，無論身穿什麼造型都展現她獨有的高級性感，還讓她獲得品牌的青睞，奪下Valentino、寶格麗的代言。"},{"pid":"3f0d79ecea974fbf0a054cd77c1458f79262024c","tid":2457672,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T23:36:10.000Z","msg":"完整名單：<br />\n<br />\nTOP1 Zendaya<br />\n<br />\nTOP 2 Jennie<br />\n<br />\nTOP 3 ViolaDavis<br />\n<br />\nTOP 4 Lupita Nyong'o<br />\n<br />\nTOP 5 Gemma Chan<br />\n<br />\nTOP 6 Saoirse Ronan<br />\n<br />\nTOP 7 EmiliaClake<br />\n<br />\nTOP 8 Scarlett Johansson<br />\n<br />\nTOP 9 Rihanna<br />\n<br />\nTOP 10 Serena Williams"},{"pid":"97d634503e2c0a42a73135b385465867424f2cb6","tid":2457672,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T23:45:50.000Z","msg":"鯰魚女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e077caf461fb3638ce8de1ad24bcc5e6c1569d59","tid":2457672,"uid":19660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d54753559238fdad72e500502ae343955e57216f","tid":2457672,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T23:35:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2021/03/22/1/11921779.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2021%2F03%2F22%2F1%2F11921779.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=2b4e279b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2021/03/22/1/11921778.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2021%2F03%2F22%2F1%2F11921778.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=a